text: Nicole Lewis (born 26 January 1989) is a New Zealand female water polo player. She competed for the New Zealand women's national water polo team in the 2013 World Aquatics Championships, 2015 World Aquatics Championships, and 2017 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * Nicole+Lewis zimbio Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand water polo players
